Privacy Policy

-

Your privacy is important to us. It is our policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect from you across our website, https://www.timschedule.com, and other sites we own and operate.

Information We Collect

-

We only collect information necessary to provide our services to you. This may include your name, email address, and other information relevant to your use of our services.

-

How We Use Your Information

-

We use the information we collect to provide, maintain, and improve our services. We do not share your information with third parties except as required by law.

-

Your Consent

-

By using our site, you consent to our privacy policy.

-

Contact Us

-

If you have any questions about our privacy policy, please contact us at [your-email@example.com].
